<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Is that not a little weird? The FDIC conducted=
 a (rather lengthy) auction for SVB=E2=80=99s assets, and the best bidder w=
as willing to pay about $13 billion less than they were worth, and the FDIC=
 was fine with that. Why?</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Well, we have talked about this too. <a href=
=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31439676.262437/aHR0cHM6L=
